    ns1:previousKnowledge """This course focuses on how to use English in professional and academic contexts, rather than on the study of English from a philological viewpoint. It is a practice-oriented course.
Certifying a B2 level of English according to the CEFRL is compulsory before enrolling for this course. The B2 language certificates accepted by the UPM can be found on https://www.etsist.upm.es/escuela/departamentos/LING/acreditacion-b2-en-lengua-ingles"""@es .

